{"tid":2296946,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"譚文豪續到黃店做義工撐黃圈：每個人都要諗吓自身可以付出幾多","createTime":"2020-11-23T01:54:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-23T04:13:04.000Z","uid":271829,"like":63,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"3a485118ceb1ff5d500a9303fc19664407bced11","tid":2296946,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T01:54:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/KECmtxV6iSr7uHkcNseuz7huF0w=/5544x3614/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6DBJTOIFAFAT7I3OMSC63ANUQE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FKECmtxV6iSr7uHkcNseuz7huF0w%3D%2F5544x3614%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6DBJTOIFAFAT7I3OMSC63ANUQE.jpg&h=df05bed9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不少有留意其Facebook的巿民，早已排隊到場光顧支持。本報記者攝<br />\n...<br />\n公民黨立法會議員譚文豪本月中與民主派總辭，抗議人大理DQ4名民主派議員後，今午落區化身腸粉師傅，為佐敦黃店做義工，不少巿民聞風而至光顧，店外大排長龍。<br />\n譚文豪接受《蘋果》專訪時表示，香港人支持黃色經濟圈十分重要，表明「即使我係唔係議員身份，我做得幾多，我都會去幫」。他指，港人透過代議士發聲的渠道消失後，「每個人都要化整為零，都要諗吓自身可以付出幾多，去捍衞自已嘅權益同屋企人」。<br />\n<br />\n稱黃色經濟圈成港人僅有發聲渠道<br />\n晉身立法會前為民航機師的譚文豪，今午現身佐敦黃店「濃姐石磨腸粉」化身腸粉師傅，不少有留意其Facebook的巿民到場光顧支持。譚文豪受訪時表示，早在辭任議員前，已答應為該店出任義工，因在政府多方打壓下，黃色經濟圈成為香港人僅有的發聲渠道，亦為同路人創造了很多就業機會，表明「即使我係唔係議員身份，我做得幾多，我都會去幫」，目標是將黃圈「越做越闊、越做越深」。<br />\n...<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201122/HV7T4RUM4RESNLXZW3TE4SLA4Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201122%2FHV7T4RUM4RESNLXZW3TE4SLA4Q%2F&d=icC9UeWzMg70WCHWfTItT08L9AbO9EvXEPTzVQ1jYSs%3D&h=858ac301\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201122%2FHV7T4RUM4RESNLXZW3TE4SLA4Q%2F&h=531f23ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201122/HV7T4RUM4RESNLXZW3TE4SLA4Q/</a>"},{"pid":"09b36e190aee5c9edcfda621d8ecd27d178111ac","tid":2296946,"uid":125026,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T01:58:05.000Z","msg":"每個人都有好多嘢做到，係你唔做，定懶得做？"},{"pid":"b756ed6283b767c617d817acdf4ae342fa42706f","tid":2296946,"uid":49669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T02:00:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c542289fffe3c03a6a4b192c6aea5bbc2a53eaf9","tid":2296946,"uid":125026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T02:02:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"036d85b7d2d5b51598c34304bb4b3b8e106f0d63","tid":2296946,"uid":284432,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T02:08:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"949ac2c7b0c81249d56cb929a0ddefc24f7aec81","tid":2296946,"uid":115579,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T02:10:12.000Z","msg":"幫班人講埋 <br />\n做show <br />\n選票"},{"pid":"ced74b3479f38d0cdd14fe528b958a9139693cd1","tid":2296946,"uid":27432,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T02:10:22.000Z","msg":"好人黎既佢係"},{"pid":"a6a569d8a7b37997b46813434168cf220c4a09ba","tid":2296946,"uid":4917,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T02:18:43.000Z","msg":"「譚文豪先後被國泰及立法會裁走後，無工可做，淪為食肆店員」<br />\n<br />\n幫文匯諗埋標題"},{"pid":"a7ccc098cdab02f6a71d665f3c8c9174cfb5619c","tid":2296946,"uid":290393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a485118ceb1ff5d500a9303fc19664407bced11","tid":2296946,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T01:54:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/KECmtxV6iSr7uHkcNseuz7huF0w=/5544x3614/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6DBJTOIFAFAT7I3OMSC63ANUQE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FKECmtxV6iSr7uHkcNseuz7huF0w%3D%2F5544x3614%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6DBJTOIFAFAT7I3OMSC63ANUQE.jpg&h=df05bed9&s={SIZE}\" />